Provides: python (= 2.7.100)
Replaces: python (>= 2.7), python-minimal (>= 2.7)
Conflicts: python (<< 2.7.100), python-minimal (<< 2.7.100)
Description: Simple package to provide python2 wrapper with python3
 This package allows installing packages depending on 'python'
 By default python is a transitional package pointing to Python2.
 This package provides 'pip' and 'python'.
